      "name": "第五味：青春 (Fifth Flavor: Youth)",
      "theme": "Modern youth's reflection on heritage",
      "content": {
        "story": "In this rapidly changing era, how do we maintain connection with our ancestors? Lei Cha is not just a beverage, but a way of inheritance.",
